Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標丟棄推進器了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TFS66th 205 207 落空
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TAS47th 進入27區域
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油機 前往A27
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A27 了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急下降後接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度3000英呎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,105 重覆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼隊長 交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動誘導裝置 鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射熱導引飛彈\N發射熱導引飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼3號被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方很厲害...\N進行交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.52,0:04:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼4號 進行交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動誘導裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後面 快散開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開 散開 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動誘導裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射熱導引飛彈\N發射熱導引飛彈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方很厲害 對方很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開 散開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼2號 切掉油管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滅火 食屍鬼2號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食屍鬼2號 快回答\N食屍鬼2號
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擊落了三分之一是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是悽慘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦姆又提高機動性性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去了 深井少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是特殊戰3號機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-3雪風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情報收集行動 結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有發現生存者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務完成 RTB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死神...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 捕捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.65,0:06:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機首方位29 朝我們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120秒後交錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直線朝這裡衝過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IFF沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上昇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我們打嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能是友機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是IFF故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.37,0:07:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SUPER SYLPH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同型機 不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧 深井少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是SYLPH
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快取得連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方把線路關掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 他就是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你在做什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪風...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說他是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23號跑道 緊急關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FSQ 4.21清除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4.21清除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 零
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快連絡醫療小組
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔架 快拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搬下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(任務完成)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是B-3所記錄下來的\N不明機體影影像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.47,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是\N地球型SUPER SYLPH
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機型完全相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明機體連殘骸骸\N都沒有發現是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟脫出的後座乘員一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也尚未接到未歸隊機的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 隆勃特上校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據記錄表示
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用了肉眼確認後\N才開始進行交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難道沒想過這可能是友機嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深井少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為它叫我開火\N所以我就開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果雪風這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它就是...迦姆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他們的表情了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些地方一定被你說中 了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.11,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暫時不能飛而已\N忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的\N我會好好操你一番的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣多少可以分散注意力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以為選擇了\N不用飛行的輕鬆生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過距離輕鬆\N似乎還遠得很
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我來一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得辦個派對才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見面時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把青豆跟桃子混在一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得這傢伙的吃法\N真是讓人看了就有氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我曾祈禱 希望不要讓\N這種傢伙分發到我的隊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.12,0:14:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本就不像是吃飯時的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃或難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就感覺不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很想知道這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的痊癒慶祝會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來要寫悔過書了 傑克
